1003
00:33:54,716 --> 00:33:55,815
- can be a disadvantage. - Right.

1004
00:33:55,816 --> 00:33:57,645
- Looking at your photo, Seung Yoon, - A small face can be an advantage.

1005
00:33:57,646 --> 00:34:00,085
I can see that you really are naturally muscular.

1006
00:34:00,086 --> 00:34:02,686
I'm sure he's been working out hard,

1007
00:34:02,786 --> 00:34:04,825
but his muscles are...

1008
00:34:04,826 --> 00:34:06,996
- They're good. They're so pretty. - in such good shape.

1009
00:34:07,226 --> 00:34:10,996
- My head is... - He's got muscles like a textbook.

1010
00:34:11,666 --> 00:34:12,995
And he's good at martial arts too.

1011
00:34:12,996 --> 00:34:15,335
Tell us about how you started martial arts.

1012
00:34:15,336 --> 00:34:16,536
You fought in a game.

1013
00:34:17,166 --> 00:34:19,166
I don't really want to talk about martial arts, but...

1014
00:34:19,306 --> 00:34:21,475
- I was working out hard... - Right.

1015
00:34:21,476 --> 00:34:23,605
- on "Gym Boy" at the time. - I saw it on YouTube.

1016
00:34:23,606 --> 00:34:25,606
I had this healthy image back then.

1017
00:34:25,946 --> 00:34:29,816
It was Korea's first mixed martial arts match in a long time.

1018
00:34:29,976 --> 00:34:31,545
And they needed a special event.

1019
00:34:31,546 --> 00:34:33,016
So they asked me to participate in it.

1020
00:34:33,146 --> 00:34:35,416
I dreamed of being a professional wrestler when I was young.

1021
00:34:35,756 --> 00:34:37,385
I wanted to be a pro wrestler.

1022
00:34:37,386 --> 00:34:39,786
So as soon as they asked me, I accepted.

1023
00:34:39,986 --> 00:34:41,556
But there were only two months left to prepare.

1024
00:34:41,896 --> 00:34:44,326
I have a disadvantage because my arms are short.

1025
