It's a disadvantage because I can't reach the opponent.

1026
00:34:47,266 --> 00:34:48,465
- It's so cute though. - I know.

1027
00:34:48,466 --> 00:34:49,665
- It looks so cute already. - He's so cute.

1028
00:34:49,666 --> 00:34:51,305
- It's hard to reach the opponent. - Right.

1029
00:34:51,306 --> 00:34:52,306
Once you land a punch on him,
- it can make him groggy. - Right.

1030
00:34:53,406 --> 00:34:55,275
I would strike if I could reach, but I couldn't.

1031
00:34:55,276 --> 00:34:58,375
So I tried grabbing the opponent's leg and turn him over.

1032
00:34:58,376 --> 00:35:00,846
- You went for ground techniques. - I was going for ground fighting.

1033
00:35:01,076 --> 00:35:03,416
On the day of the competition, I felt so good.

1034
00:35:03,546 --> 00:35:04,845
I was under the spotlight.

1035
00:35:04,846 --> 00:35:07,656
Like the pro wrestlers I admired when I was young,

1036
00:35:07,816 --> 00:35:09,556
I entered with loud cheers.

1037
00:35:09,786 --> 00:35:11,085
I was in good physical shape too.

1038
00:35:11,086 --> 00:35:12,656
And I wasn't wearing a top.

1039
00:35:12,886 --> 00:35:14,596
One player told me this before I went up on the ring.

1040
00:35:15,056 --> 00:35:17,065
He said that even if I got struck during a fight,

1041
00:35:17,066 --> 00:35:18,426
- my body would release adrenaline. - Right.

1042
00:35:18,626 --> 00:35:20,125
- So I wouldn't feel pain from it. - You don't feel pain.

1043
00:35:20,126 --> 00:35:22,065
- They say you can't feel pain. - That's what's interesting.

1044
00:35:22,066 --> 00:35:25,566
But I would feel the pain when I came down the ring after the fight.

1045
00:35:25,706 --> 00:35:27,936
