1050
00:35:36,876 --> 00:35:38,285
- Something's coming up. - I thought to myself.

1051
00:35:38,286 --> 00:35:39,946
- "So this is adrenaline." - Goodness.

1052
00:35:40,086 --> 00:35:42,056
I was worked up. I thought I was all ready.

1053
00:35:42,156 --> 00:35:43,856
The bell rang as soon as I went on the ring.

1054
00:35:44,256 --> 00:35:46,386
I approached the opponent in a cool way like this.

1055
00:35:46,586 --> 00:35:47,856
- I was hit right here. - Right.

1056
00:35:48,296 --> 00:35:52,096
It was so painful.

1057
00:35:52,496 --> 00:35:53,665
- Adrenaline didn't work? - Seriously.

1058
00:35:53,666 --> 00:35:54,866
Adrenaline was...

1059
00:35:56,536 --> 00:35:58,536
It really hurt.

1060
00:35:59,506 --> 00:36:01,575
I was running out of adrenaline,

1061
00:36:01,576 --> 00:36:03,206
