1107
00:37:36,366 --> 00:37:38,605
Everywhere. But the important thing was this.

1108
00:37:38,606 --> 00:37:41,676
I saw his knee approaching me very slowly like this.

1109
00:37:41,936 --> 00:37:43,176
- Right in front of my eyes. - Right.

1110
00:37:43,376 --> 00:37:46,245
Right in front of my eyes, his knee was flying toward me.

1111
00:37:46,246 --> 00:37:47,446
