- He knew it. - He saw it.

1146
00:39:07,056 --> 00:39:08,596
He knew that you were just saying it.

1147
00:39:08,756 --> 00:39:10,455
The ones who want to continue...

1148
00:39:10,456 --> 00:39:12,126
- would lift up their fists. - But you...

1149
00:39:12,626 --> 00:39:13,726
