1152
00:39:19,736 --> 00:39:20,775
- You did a great job. - I thought...

1153
00:39:20,776 --> 00:39:21,835
It would be more fun to watch the match...

1154
00:39:21,836 --> 00:39:22,875
- since I heard the story. - Seung Yoon.

1155
00:39:22,876 --> 00:39:24,076
- I hope you don't watch it. - Gosh.

1156
00:39:24,646 --> 00:39:26,445
